==English==
===Etymology===
Latin ''[[mergere]]''
===Verb===
'''to merge'''  ([[merges]], [[merged]], [[merging]])

# Combine or be combined into a whole.
# Blend gradually into something else.

===Related terms===
* [[merger]]

====Synonyms====
*[[amalgamate]]
*[[combine]]
*[[conflate]]
*[[intergrate]]
*[[unite]]

